# Naming e Design System

## Naming file e directory
```
components/  → PascalCase:          MaterialeCard.tsx, VerbaleWizard.tsx
hooks/       → camelCase + use:     useAuth.ts, useOnlineStatus.ts
services/    → PascalCase+Service:  OneDriveService.ts, ProveService.ts
utils/       → camelCase:           naming.ts, saluto.ts
pages/       → PascalCase+Page:     DashboardPage.tsx, RegistroPage.tsx
config/      → camelCase:           env.ts, msal.config.ts, moduleRegistry.ts
db/          → PascalCase+dominio:  VerbaleDB.ts, SyncQueue.ts
```

## Naming variabili
```typescript
// ✅ Boolean con prefisso is/has/can/should
const isLoading = true; const hasError = false
const canSubmit = form.isValid && !isLoading
const isOnline = navigator.onLine

// ✅ Array con nome plurale
const verbali = await db.verbali.toArray()
const prove   = await proveService.leggi(cantiereId)

// ✅ Handler con handle prefix
const handleAvanza = () => setStep(s => s + 1)
const handleFieldChange = (key: string, value: string) => { ... }
const handleArchivia = async () => { ... }
```

